DOC.brief_summary: The purpose of this study is to learn more about how AZD1305 is handled by the body, i.e the absorption, distribution, metabolism and excretion of AZD1305.
DOC.brief_title: To Study the Absorption, Distribution, Metabolism and Excretion of AZD1305
DOC.criteria: Healthy volunteers A body mass index (BMI=weight/height2) of 19 to 30 kg/m2 Potassium outside normal reference values ECG findings outside normal range
